{"tid":680438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外傭組織示威要求容海恩公開道歉","createTime":"2018-05-27T07:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T08:48:15.000Z","uid":60545,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a50e403da7bdd6c2e674c4b28da1f3db632f7dab","tid":680438,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有外傭組織發起遊行，抗議新民黨立法會議員容海恩發表歧視外傭言論，容海恩接收他們的請願信，但未有回應會否公開就事件道歉。<br />\n<br />\n容海恩在立法會大會這一番言論，惹來大量在港的外傭不滿，要求她道歉。<br />\n<br />\n逾二百名外傭遊行手持印有容海恩照片的橫額及示威道具，從中環遮打道出發。她們遊行到灣仔新民黨總部，容海恩出來接收請願信。<br />\n<br />\n遊行發起人指，兩人交談時，容海恩有向他們道歉，但當他再要求容海恩公開道歉，她就未肯承諾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=307246&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307246%26refer%3D&d=ScJHb5btZNdrEc9xxEec%2FrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=c863572a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307246%26refer%3D&h=6b053fe4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=307246&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"8e8a2dedc675f4650133cd1c9627fc10a8379166","tid":680438,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"今個星期日熱騰騰，坐街會熱死，行下無咁熱"},{"pid":"4eaddec4bec48442b177eeafb88b7445436ab4e0","tid":680438,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"人地配有民主，香港人甘願做奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}